[SN]TITLE[SN]
Balbeggie death treated as suspicious

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A police investigation is under way into the suspicious death of a 49-year-old man in Perthshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The man was discovered after officers were called to an address in Croft Park, Balbeggie, at about noon on Thursday.
Police Scotland said next of kin have been made aware and inquiries were at an early stage.
They urged anyone with any information to contact them.
